### Fixed:
 - [fpavogt, 2022-01-27] Fix #66 and #67.
 - [fpavogt, 2022-01-26] Fix #62, #63 and #64.
### Changed:
 - [fpavogt, 2022-02-01] Implement review feedback, including name change for `scaled` to `apply_scaling`.

## [v0.2.1.dev0]
